<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased API Error Rates and Latencies>
Between 7:49AM PDT and 8:27AM PDT EC2 experienced elevated API errors for instance related APIs in a single Availability Zone in the US-EAST-1 region. Existing instances were not affected. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
